{
  "id": "RAW_8dc453",
  "title": "CodeBuddy Code，我愿称之为第一个国产 Claude Code",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247498955&idx=1&sn=f816b49d00fd9c3e47e3ffd6b740d69f",
  "date": "2025-09-10 01:39:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天我非常激动，等了好久，终于等到了！ 终于有国内用户可以方便使用的</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">Claude Code的替代品了！国产AI编程，雄起了！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它是 CodeBuddy Code。腾讯CodeBuddy团队低调推出的一款类Claude Code的cli产品。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">&nbsp;免费公测，无需邀请码</span>。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在它之前，最佳使用国产技术平替Claude Code的方法是： 使用Claude Code的客户端，然后选择国内模型，比如GLM 4.5、Kimi K2、DeepSeek 3.1等等。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些平替方案最大的问题是 —— 模型不支持多模态，不能识别用户给的图片。CodeBuddy没有这个问题， 因为它支持选择所有世界顶级的多模态模型。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们多了一个方便的靠谱选择。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);\">省流版</span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">CodeBuddy Code的优势？</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ul&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;list-style-type: circle;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:null},&quot;listitem&quot;,{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">可以使用Gemini-pro-2.5模型和<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Claude-sonnet-4.0</span>模型</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">非常舍得花Token</span>，不会像Cursor一样为了省Token而牺牲效果、偷偷压缩上下文。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">不会像Claude Code一样因为节点网络问题而封号</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">暂时免费</span>。据说未来支持收费时，会支持微信支付，无需海外信用卡。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">速度极快</span>，竟然比我直接使用Claude Code更快</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ul&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;list-style-type: circle;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:null},&quot;listitem&quot;,{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">可以切换<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">多家厂商模型</span>，不像Claude Code或Codex只能选择自家模型。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">比起Claude Code还缺少什么？</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">暂不支持Claude-Opus-4.1模型（不过Gemini-pro-2.5很强，可以弥补）</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">暂不支持Agent功能</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">暂不支持后台任务</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">暂不支持</span><span leaf=\"\">HTTP/SSE协议的MCP。（非常可惜！）</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">避坑必读</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">请一定要使用国际版！</span>( 配置普普通通的网络魔法即可）。因为国内版只有DeepSeek 3.1模型，国际版才能使用Claude-4.0和Gemini-pro-2.5模型</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">整体评价</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以用于实战</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">不方便使用官方正版Claude Code的用户，可放心选CodeBuddy Code作为平替！</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">希望它能够早点收费。免费的不够用。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);\">安装</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">执行 &nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n   <li></li>\n  </ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"nginx\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">npm</span>&nbsp;install -g&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">@tencent</span>-ai/codebuddy-code</span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin: 0pt 0pt 6pt 16.8pt;text-indent: -16.8pt;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015162\" data-ratio=\"0.7305555555555555\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=514fb814&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHBfiaD9EKxfwYyd5dUzpBLGLicoAJRZZp8hNwZXVEO92n1mLzoH1uOOcuSJr5pw6U9JIbTLSsYwtjQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我选择了Google登录。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">注意：此时一定要用魔法，打开TUN模式。否则可能会使用国内版。我们要用国际版。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);\">配置</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">这一项比较关键，和Claude Code不同，CodeBuddy Code把很多重要的内容隐藏到了 /config 里，每一个选项我们都可以研究一下。&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">我推荐你至少研究以下两个：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">第一，使用 /config 选中model，点击回车切换模型。推荐用Gemini-2.5-pro，如果是UI类工作，可以切换为Claude-4.0模型。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015165\" data-ratio=\"0.2861111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=49a4cbb2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHBfiaD9EKxfwYyd5dUzpBLGXNcHVpHyfhBeTKDicsgGTpNzmlOwDyrAatNoGFdOKQlEZxD4QYYuMng%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二，在 /config&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">关闭</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">Auto-compact 自动压缩上下文&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">【重要，编码效果提升明显】</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015166\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2712962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=49dde50b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHBfiaD9EKxfwYyd5dUzpBLGlC6Guv4d6PsybIT74iaWU2ibibkCicUmZ4ZzCOdN4ZyGhNerGp6v7rGggw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);\">初步测试</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用 /init 初始化项目</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015167\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6314814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5e496c7a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHBfiaD9EKxfwYyd5dUzpBLGzYw8DA2vC1PpSffE1vBwS6iaWhWwKgJsNcLLHibqWxQ5Cp2RfNp2e8mQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">会自动生成一个叫 CODEBUDDY.md的文件</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015168\" data-ratio=\"0.4640198511166253\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"806\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d6300dca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHBfiaD9EKxfwYyd5dUzpBLGAibjWzmBX2FR4aqyEtyjq5dupasqykicTAZq6ic9jaWKqAO91nBbYvmaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">非常舍得花token，一个初始化命令，消耗了400K token</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015169\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5814814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=71963a0a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHBfiaD9EKxfwYyd5dUzpBLG5xmzVlEd0NUt3M8djUibB2GFt9s8jjLjWmX1tDF6UEOpc6gQMibn6MFw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);\">复杂任务</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们试试稍微复杂一点的任务：让它告诉我有三位字母的.ai域名有哪些可以注册？</span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用 domain-tools 中的工具,帮我查看三位字母的所有.ai域名是否可用</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它开始自动根据现有工具和新需求，写新工具。&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">工具写完的时候，已经花了828.7k token，太舍得了，佩服！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后它开始启动工具，进行扫描</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015172\" data-ratio=\"0.5916666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2a759af2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHBfiaD9EKxfwYyd5dUzpBLGog76OnD24icQbnMwgLkfgMERhiaLuEuvlGxcqqr4hfSMp2XMWXVdibBibQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">扫描完成，帮我们发现了所有可以注册3字母.ai域名！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">请看右下角，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">这个任务一共花了3.5M token。真的很舍得花！叹为观止。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果我们是自己调用Claude-sonnet-4.0的API，就这一下子，3.5M token，小十美金就没了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015173\" data-ratio=\"0.601679104477612\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2144\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5129b596&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHBfiaD9EKxfwYyd5dUzpBLGC0hHbuT4JB7RrHt0rXB0PXVI5p3bUFwDW2lLxDyOIuhuPl3jXrkGZQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);\">查看积分消耗情况</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">打开<a href=\"https://www.codebuddy.ai/profile/usage\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.codebuddy.ai/profile/usage</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以查看积分消耗情况</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在刚才的操作里，一共消耗了 3.5M token，折算成CodeBuddy的积分，只消耗了75积分。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里的Token，包括输入、输出、缓存等等。在Claude Code里是分开统计的，CodeBuddy合并到一起了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015174\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.45925925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2f4d6e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHBfiaD9EKxfwYyd5dUzpBLGArSXQGoWuQwIppOFWPuzY8C2g24mH3D4uSIiaWMZOiavHnVoHaB3iaojw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);\">测试MCP</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">我想试试这篇文章里推荐的MCP</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247498796&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=2e3070dfaa88d96497d46d71d61a0b56&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"别再花钱买RPA了！Claude Code 实现邮件、社媒、内容创作、竞品跟踪全自动化\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">别再花钱买RPA了！Claude Code 实现邮件、社媒、内容创作、竞品跟踪全自动化</span></a></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">结果发现不支持，非常可惜。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">原因是：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">CodeBuddy暂不支持</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">HTTP/SSE协议的MCP工具。 这个太遗憾了！</span>希望腾讯团队能够尽快解决。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015177\" data-ratio=\"0.45185185185185184\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=164dcfac&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHBfiaD9EKxfwYyd5dUzpBLGGciayWGCQfoCNpF5ZVpU0sjuKK5xeyVpoxS4Ep9d3Dks73jkem3qvqw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">所幸的是，有更多的主流MCP的，是被支持的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我安装了Playwright MCP、context7、sequential-thinking mcp</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015178\" data-ratio=\"0.674074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a7e4245c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHBfiaD9EKxfwYyd5dUzpBLGFwa5IQuJDxp6fgFBQiaA7pbf3P9oibv7IprzM8FJJt4OicRZFaz1Tc5DQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我让它打开Google搜索一下我自己。可以成功运行。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">命令行里出现了报错，不知道为啥，但是可以正常工作。</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">打开Google搜索刘小排</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015179\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6462962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=16554959&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHBfiaD9EKxfwYyd5dUzpBLG6pOicKPPpCwBRHcXFGpfpvZ8piagey4xaHjYFSibMTmW8xCvUK1WK49zg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015180\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.612037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=35cd9696&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHBfiaD9EKxfwYyd5dUzpBLGaUKg7f1UUBXON5E06Ziaibk3fc6ZZ9spMBdiaFs6fWv5G2n0GHA2BFYrw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);\">搜索能力</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">上网搜索,codebuddy cli正式版到底打算收费多少钱呀,迫不及待想买</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">表现相当不错。我怀疑它用了google的搜索但是没有证据。。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015181\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.45092592592592595\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=be68e15f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHBfiaD9EKxfwYyd5dUzpBLG5GMRk0urKwXJwP1GXOVc1mJHQhJRnPxmuY5emvHgN9libvwBIOPXxAQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);\">讨论UI设计</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">用ascii画出我们首页的布局</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100015182\" data-ratio=\"1.011111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8fc1f1a4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHBfiaD9EKxfwYyd5dUzpBLGKB1pjzysdSCA1BjSSxHbfTGVQCtYe3fzlVSibq1tq8SRxPsGQLHwWvg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我觉得我们的首页图片生成区域不够现代化，如果要你重新设计，如果你是乔布斯，你会怎么设计？用ascii画出3个方案</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015183\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0046296296296295\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=80ccb855&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlHBfiaD9EKxfwYyd5dUzpBLG5vLhu2rYhRSVOaT5ASM6j62XIm5sJRkGiaGAR5jTCOSfiaLu090wTRgA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);\">其他常见问题</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">到底什么时候开始收费呀？</span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">我也不知道，据小道消息是9月内。有腾讯的朋友看到文章麻烦留言回复一下，我帮你们置顶。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">免费1000积分用完了怎么办？</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ul&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;list-style-type: circle&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:null},&quot;listitem&quot;,null,&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">似乎每天会自动增加一些积分。暂时我的方法是更换新号。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">总之，初次体验感觉惊艳，用得我很爽。 让我想起了几个月前第一次使用Claude Code时候的感觉。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我作为一个同时使用正版Codex和Claude Code的用户，CodeBuddy Code竟然可以在我的电脑里有一席之地。因为它的速度很快，当我需要做单文件的简单任务，有时候等待Claude Code这位大爷干活等得我发毛，我会换上CodeBuddy Code。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">推荐给你，期待你的反馈。&nbsp;</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章详细评测了腾讯 CodeBuddy Code 作为国产 AI 编程助手的 CLI 工具，强调其多模态支持、慷慨的 Token 使用和作为 Claude Code 替代品的潜力。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章详细评测了腾讯 CodeBuddy Code 作为国产 AI 编程助手的 CLI 工具，强调其多模态支持、慷慨的 Token 使用和作为 Claude Code 替代品的潜力。",
  "summary": "本文深度评测了腾讯团队推出的 CodeBuddy Code CLI 工具，将其定位为国内用户可用的 Claude Code 替代品。文章指出 CodeBuddy Code 的显著优势在于支持 Gemini-pro-2.5 和 Claude-sonnet-4.0 等顶级多模态模型，解决了现有国产平替方案不支持图片识别的问题。作者特别强调了其在 Token 使用上的慷慨，避免了上下文压缩导致的效果下降，并提供了安装、配置（如关闭自动压缩上下文）及多项实战测试（如项目初始化、复杂工具调用、UI 设计讨论）的详细指南。尽管存在暂不支持 Claude-Opus-4.1 和 HTTP/SSE 协议 MCP 等局限，但其快速响应和多模型切换能力使其成为值得推荐的 AI 编程辅助工具。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
